<view class="container">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view class="page-title">图片压缩</view>
    <view class="page-desc">上传图片并调节压缩质量，在体积和清晰度之间快速找到平衡。</view>
  </view>

  <file-picker
    file="{{selectedFile}}"
    accept="image"
    title="选择图片"
    description="支持 JPG、PNG、WebP 格式"
    bind:selected="handleFileSelected"
  />

  <view class="card form-card {{selectedFile ? 'form-active' : ''}}">
    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-head">
        <view class="label">压缩质量</view>
        <view class="quality-pill">{{quality}}%</view>
      </view>
      <slider
        class="quality-slider"
        min="10"
        max="100"
        value="{{quality}}"
        show-value
        activeColor="#111111"
        backgroundColor="#E5E7EB"
        block-color="#111111"
        bindchanging="handleQualityChanging"
        bindchange="handleQualityChange"
      />
      <view class="field-help">建议设置在 60% - 80% 之间，兼顾清晰度与文件大小。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="notice notice-info estimate-box" wx:if="{{estimatedSizeText}}">
      <view class="notice-head">
        <view class="notice-icon">i</view>
        <view class="notice-title">压缩结果预估</view>
      </view>
      <view class="notice-row">原图大小：<text class="notice-strong">{{originalSizeText}}</text></view>
      <view class="notice-row">预计大小：<text class="notice-strong">{{estimatedSizeText}}</text></view>
      <view class="notice-row">预计减少：<text class="notice-strong">{{estimatedReduceText}}</text></view>
    </view>

    <button
      class="btn btn-primary {{!selectedFile ? 'btn-disabled' : ''}}"
      bindtap="handleSubmit"
      hover-class="btn-hover"
    >
      开始压缩
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="notice notice-subtle tips-block">
    <view class="notice-title">使用提示</view>
    <view class="notice-row">1. 质量越低，文件越小，但图片会越模糊。</view>
    <view class="notice-row">2. 不同图片内容与格式不同，最终压缩率会有差异。</view>
    <view class="notice-row">3. 压缩完成后可在“任务列表”中查看处理结果。</view>
  </view>
</view>
